{"tid":2028043,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"諗得多好 定 唔諗得多好？","createTime":"2020-05-21T15:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T03:22:54.000Z","uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"280b190649b0c2273089a80e23d3f7f7703ed35f","tid":2028043,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"覺得有時諗太多，準備得太多係多餘，無人會多謝你，亦都無人會知道。<br />\n<br />\n為自己，諗得太多又未必會發生，諗黎多舊魚，好似諗十個可能性，到頭來都只會發生一個，甚至可能唔係你諗既果十個入面既結果。為他人諗太多，到頭來唔單止無人多謝你，反而仲屌返你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係唉多情自古誰無恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4775fddfd2726b686a16e2a3c48925802c03349","tid":2028043,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"做人都係簡單啲好"},{"pid":"0abd35d93003f5e4a6c4dda482aa715a5c0730d6","tid":2028043,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4775fddfd2726b686a16e2a3c48925802c03349","tid":2028043,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"做人都係簡單啲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"我都想簡單，但係我生性就係多疑，同埋思考性好強，每睇到一d嘢個腦自然就好似將見到既果舊嘢響個腦度煎皮拆骨，反轉又反轉，由開始到結果，幾十種可能性係咁諗係咁諗，個腦d brainstorm係咁爆係咁爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db76fbe1db80e6f75b6e0a59e84540b6891737a","tid":2028043,"uid":315910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"諗得多辛苦啊"},{"pid":"23ae5782e5d68c23d98d709581e7549435a7c2ea","tid":2028043,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0abd35d93003f5e4a6c4dda482aa715a5c0730d6","tid":2028043,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4775fddfd2726b686a16e2a3c48925802c03349","tid":2028043,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"做人都係簡單啲好"},"cit